game.name: Pregnant Princesses Catwalk Show
game.description:
Your favorite cute princesses Ariel and Anna are pregnant and both have got participated in a special fashion show where only pregnant mommy can perform. Hey ladies! It is not going to be easy at all since they will also have to perform the catwalk while wearing the complete designer outfits. They have hired you as their personal fashion stylist. Join the Pregnant Princesses Catwalk Show and be prepared to help the girls to pick up the nice outfits for the competition!

Browse through their wider collection of pregnant clothes and help them get the spectacular looks for the show in this one of the best HTML dressing games for girls! Start the fun with Ariel by giving her a flower printed purple skirt with a strapless purple and orange top with two different bows! Do not forget to complete her with the needful accessories like a blue color headband with peacock feathers. Try to be fast since Anna is also waiting for her turn, friends!

Give this lady a pair of glittery purple pants and pair it with a blue corset with short puff sleeves! Accessorize her dress with a green hat with a gem and a purple bow! Make sure to choose all the products available in their wardrobe to make them look stunning and gain the attention of jury in this princess dress-up game! Try to keep mixing and matching other items as well until you prepare the jaw-dropping looks for each princess and win in the end!
